headline: Trade Desk (TTD): Reassessing Valuation After a Steep Share Price Reset
summary: Trade Desk (TTD) has been under pressure lately, with the stock sliding about 11% over the past month and roughly 66% year to date, even as revenue and earnings continue to grow.
